r8684 | kmr44 | 2023-01-28 09:58:51 +0000 (Sat, 28 Jan 2023) | 15 lines

Added files containing details for all Schizosaccharomyces PDB entries

These files come from the PDBe Advanced search form:
https://www.ebi.ac.uk/pdbe/entry/search/index/?advancedSearch%3Atrue

by searching for all entries with genus "schizosaccharomyces"

the result page:
https://www.ebi.ac.uk/pdbe/entry/search/index/?searchParams=%7B%22q_genus%22:%5B%7B%22value%22:%22schizosaccharomyces%22,%22condition1%22:%22AND%22,%22condition2%22:%22Contains%22%7D%5D,%22resultState%22:%7B%22tabIndex%22:0,%22paginationIndex%22:1,%22perPage%22:%2210%22,%22sortBy%22:%22Sort%20by%22%7D%7D

Using the Download button, and selecting all columns

See: https://github.com/pombase/website/issues/1997
